title: Juno Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Italian, Mediterranean, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Israeli, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cafe at Milano Square offering marked vegan items on the menu, including a vegan breakfast plus sandwiches, salads, Italian dishes. Intimate atmosphere, next to Juno Wine, and you can order from that wine list in the afternoon and evening. No extra charge for soy milk in coffee. Business lunch deals Sun-Thur 12-5pm.
